Urutare rwa Ndaba ni urutare ruherereye ku muhanda uva mu karere ka Muhanga ujya mu karere ka Karongi,mu birometero makumyabiri(20km) uvuye mu mugi wa karongi, uru rutare rumanukaho amazi menshi, bivugwa ko rwitiriwe umugabo witwa Ndaba wakundaga akaryoshye cyane ariko ubuki. Bivugwa cyane n'abahatuye ko uyu mugabo yajyanye nabagenzi be guhakura ubuki bw'inzuki zabaga mu mwobo wari hagati kuri urwo rutare, maze bakomwoherezayo ngo abazanire ubuki, aho guhakura ngo abikire bagenzi be agahakura yirira maze barambiwe baramurekura yikubita mu manga yuru rutare rurerure rufite hafi metero ijana z'ubujyakuzimu.[https://igihe.com/umuco/amateka/amwe-mu-mateka-y-urutare-rwa-ndaba] 

== Amateka ==
Urutare rwa Ndaba ruri mu hantu nyaburanga  mu [[Rwanda]] kandi hakurura abakerarugendo cyane, benshi basura uru rutare rumanukaho amazi meza y'urwererane rufite n'amateka atangaza benshi.

Uko urutare rwa ndaba rurushaho kugenda rwamamara niko benshi mu bakerarugendo barushaho kuhasura cyane, ibi byatumye benshi mu bana bo mu karere ka karongi, umurenge wa Rubengera, bata ishuri bakajya kubwira amateka yuru rutare abakerarugendo mu ndimi zitandukanye harimo mu kinyarwanda, icyongereza ndetse n'igiswahiri.[http://popote.rw/bataye-ishuri-bahitamo-kujya-basobanura-amateka-yurutare-rwa-ndaba/]

