== Igihe rumaze ==
Nta gihe runaka kizwi uru rutare rwa ndaba rwaba rumaze, abahatuye bakuze ndetse banahavukiye nibo bavuga amateka yaho,nabo bavuga ko bavutse ruhari kandi ko nabo bakuze bumva inkuru y'umugabo ndaba wazize inda mbi no kutuzuza umugambi cyangwa inama yagiranye na bagenzi be bikarangira aguye ku birenge byuru rutare agapfa.<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dp3MBsFH_o4</ref>

